1
00:00:07,667 --> 00:00:09,291
- EARTH.

2
00:00:09,333 --> 00:00:11,125
FIRE.

3
00:00:11,166 --> 00:00:12,875
AIR.

4
00:00:12,917 --> 00:00:15,083
WATER.

5
00:00:15,125 --> 00:00:19,125
ONLY THE AVATAR CAN MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

6
00:00:19,166 --> 00:00:22,083
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

7
00:00:27,166 --> 00:00:29,083
- THE EARTH EMPIRE HAS INVADED
THE UNITED REPUBLIC!

8
00:00:29,125 --> 00:00:31,291
AFTER KUVIRA
DEMONSTRATED THE POWER

9
00:00:31,333 --> 00:00:33,583
OF HER SPIRIT ENERGY WEAPON,
PRESIDENT RAIKO

10
00:00:33,625 --> 00:00:35,375
SURRENDERED THE CITY,
BUT THE AVATAR REFUSED

11
00:00:35,417 --> 00:00:37,041
TO GIVE UP
WITHOUT A FIGHT.

12
00:00:37,083 --> 00:00:39,458
KORRA HELD BAATAR JR. HOSTAGE,
HOPING TO FORCE KUVIRA

13
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,542
TO BACK DOWN,
BUT THE PLAN FAILED,

14
00:00:41,583 --> 00:00:43,542
AND SHE FIRED
ON TEAM AVATAR'S HIDEOUT.

15
00:00:43,583 --> 00:00:47,000
CAN ANYTHING OR ANYONE
STOP KUVIRA AND HER MECHA-GIANT?

16
00:00:57,834 --> 00:01:00,834
- [grunting]

17
00:01:03,083 --> 00:01:04,542
GO AHEAD. TAKE YOUR TIME.

18
00:01:04,583 --> 00:01:06,208
JUST BENDING A GIANT WALL.

19
00:01:06,250 --> 00:01:08,250
MAN, WE GOT A LOT
OF PEOPLE HERE.

20
00:01:08,291 --> 00:01:10,125
IS THAT EVERYBODY?

21
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:11,709
[grunts]

22
00:01:13,375 --> 00:01:16,333
[suspenseful music]

23
00:01:16,375 --> 00:01:20,750
♪ ♪

24
00:01:20,792 --> 00:01:23,709
[electronic grinding]

25
00:01:25,083 --> 00:01:26,333
- [gasps]

26
00:01:28,250 --> 00:01:30,625
KUVIRA'S HEADING OUR WAY
WITH A PLATOON OF MECHA-SUITS.

27
00:01:30,667 --> 00:01:31,834
- WHAT SHOULD WE DO?

28
00:01:31,875 --> 00:01:33,750
THIS IS MY HOMETOWN,
AND I HATE TO SAY IT,

29
00:01:33,792 --> 00:01:35,417
BUT THERE'S NO USE RISKING
ALL OUR LIVES

30
00:01:35,458 --> 00:01:36,667
TO FIGHT THAT GIANT THING.

31
00:01:36,709 --> 00:01:38,041
LET HER TAKE THE CITY
FOR NOW.

32
00:01:38,083 --> 00:01:40,208
WE'LL THINK OF SOME WAY
TO COME BACK AND BEAT HER.

33
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:42,625
- WHAT ABOUT ALL THE PEOPLE
WHO HAVEN'T BEEN EVACUATED YET?

34
00:01:42,667 --> 00:01:44,291
IF KUVIRA FINDS OUT
WU IS WITH THEM,

35
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:46,125
SHE MIGHT FIRE
THAT SPIRIT CANNON AT HIM

36
00:01:46,166 --> 00:01:47,625
AND TAKE THEM ALL OUT.

37
00:01:47,667 --> 00:01:50,041
- I COULDN'T STOP KUVIRA
FROM TAKING ZAOFU.

38
00:01:50,083 --> 00:01:52,500
I'M NOT LETTING HER CONQUER
REPUBLIC CITY.

39
00:01:52,542 --> 00:01:55,166
THE WORLD ISN'T SAFE AS LONG
AS SHE HAS THAT WEAPON.

40
00:01:55,208 --> 00:01:56,208
- I AGREE.

41
00:01:56,250 --> 00:01:58,041
WE TAKE DOWN THAT GIANT TODAY.

42
00:01:58,083 --> 00:01:59,750
- LIN!

43
00:01:59,792 --> 00:02:01,125
- GLAD TO SEE
YOU ALL MADE IT OUT.

44
00:02:01,166 --> 00:02:02,542
YOU HAD ME WORRIED.

45
00:02:02,583 --> 00:02:04,709
- WELL, YOU BENDERS ARE GONNA
HAVE TO FIGHT HER ALONE.

46
00:02:04,750 --> 00:02:07,834
SHE JUST BLEW UP OUR FACTORY
WITH ALL OUR HUMMINGBIRD SUITS.

47
00:02:07,875 --> 00:02:09,208
- NOT ALL OF THEM.

48
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:11,625
THERE ARE THE PROTOTYPES
BACK AT MY OFFICE.

49
00:02:11,667 --> 00:02:13,166
IF WE CAN GET THOSE
READY TO FLY,

50
00:02:13,208 --> 00:02:15,542
WE'LL AT LEAST BE ABLE
TO OFFER A LITTLE AIR SUPPORT.

51
00:02:15,583 --> 00:02:18,083
- SU, YOU TAKE BAATAR JR.
AND THE REST OF THE WOUNDED

52
00:02:18,125 --> 00:02:19,500
BACK TO ASAMI'S OFFICE.

53
00:02:19,542 --> 00:02:21,250
GET THOSE SUITS WORKING
AS SOON AS YOU CAN.

54
00:02:21,291 --> 00:02:24,375
THE REST OF US WILL JUST
HAVE TO FACE KUVIRA ON OUR OWN.

55
00:02:24,417 --> 00:02:27,583
[crowd chattering]

56
00:02:29,625 --> 00:02:31,792
- EVERYONE, PLEASE SETTLE DOWN.

57
00:02:31,834 --> 00:02:34,667
THE TRAINS SHOULD BE RETURNING
TO PICK US UP SOON.

58
00:02:34,709 --> 00:02:36,500
- TELL THAT MECHA-JERK
TO SETTLE DOWN.

59
00:02:36,542 --> 00:02:38,542
SHE'S THE ONE BLOWING UP
THE WHOLE CITY!

60
00:02:38,583 --> 00:02:40,959
- I HATE TO BE THE BEARER
OF MORE BAD NEWS,

61
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:44,333
BUT I JUST HEARD ON THE RADIO
THAT KUVIRA'S ARMY

62
00:02:44,375 --> 00:02:45,875
HAS DESTROYED THE TRAIN TRACKS.

63
00:02:45,917 --> 00:02:48,625
WE'RE NOT GETTING OUT
OF THE CITY BY RAIL.

64
00:02:48,667 --> 00:02:51,333
- EVERYONE, I WAS JUST
UP ON THE OBSERVATION DECK

65
00:02:51,375 --> 00:02:53,875
AND SAW A BUNCH OF MECHA-SUIT
SOLDIERS HEADING THIS WAY!

66
00:02:53,917 --> 00:02:56,834
- OH, GREAT!
THE GIANT ONE WASN'T ENOUGH?

67
00:02:56,875 --> 00:02:58,166
IT'S OVER!

68
00:02:58,208 --> 00:02:59,875
WE'RE ALL
GONNA GET BLOWN TO BITS!

69
00:02:59,917 --> 00:03:01,125
- LISTEN, EVERYONE.

70
00:03:01,166 --> 00:03:03,208
I CAN GET US OUT OF HERE
IF YOU JUST SIT TIGHT.

71
00:03:03,250 --> 00:03:04,542
CAN YOU STEP OFF
THE BENCH, PLEASE?

72
00:03:04,583 --> 00:03:05,750
IT'S A LITTLE CROWDED UP HERE.

73
00:03:05,792 --> 00:03:07,542
- SURE.
I'M ONLY THE CONDUCTOR.

74
00:03:07,583 --> 00:03:10,083
NO ONE NEEDS ME ON THE BENCH.

75
00:03:10,125 --> 00:03:11,417
- JUST STAY CALM.

76
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:13,083
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK. COME ON!

77
00:03:13,125 --> 00:03:15,208
- WHOA! WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

78
00:03:15,250 --> 00:03:16,792
- I'M GOING TO GET SOME HELP.

79
00:03:16,834 --> 00:03:18,500
YOU THINK YOU CAN HANDLE
THIS UNRULY MOB

80
00:03:18,542 --> 00:03:19,750
FOR A LITTLE WHILE?

81
00:03:19,792 --> 00:03:21,125
- I RAISED MEELO.

82
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:22,834
I CAN HANDLE ANYTHING.

83
00:03:22,875 --> 00:03:25,834
[suspenseful music]

84
00:03:25,875 --> 00:03:29,959
♪ ♪

85
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,250
- A PAINT STORE?
THAT'S IT!

86
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:35,667
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING, MEELO?

87
00:03:35,709 --> 00:03:38,083
- I JUST GOT AN IDEA
HOW TO BEAT THE GIANT!

88
00:03:38,125 --> 00:03:42,291
NOW EVERYONE, GRAB SOME PAINT
AND FIND ME SOME BALLOONS!

89
00:03:42,333 --> 00:03:45,250
[mechanical grinding]

90
00:04:00,166 --> 00:04:01,333
- AIRBENDERS APPROACHING.

91
00:04:01,375 --> 00:04:03,542
- I SEE THEM.

92
00:04:03,583 --> 00:04:05,375
[mechanical grinding]

93
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:19,291
[electrical booming]

94
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:21,250
[all cry out]

95
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,417
[explosion]

96
00:04:24,458 --> 00:04:27,667
[suspenseful music]

97
00:04:27,709 --> 00:04:35,625
♪ ♪

98
00:04:49,875 --> 00:04:51,709
- BOMBS AWAY!

99
00:05:07,417 --> 00:05:09,333
- CLEAR THE GLASS.

100
00:05:14,709 --> 00:05:15,667
- NOW!

101
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:21,875
- THE JOINTS ARE PLATINUM, TOO!

102
00:05:21,917 --> 00:05:24,750
WE CAN'T METALBEND ANY OF IT!

103
00:05:24,792 --> 00:05:27,291
- YOU'RE ABOUT TO GET
THE WORLD'S LARGEST HOT-FOOT,

104
00:05:27,333 --> 00:05:28,500
METAL LADY!

105
00:05:38,208 --> 00:05:39,583
- [grunts]

106
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:49,208
- HIT IT NOW!

107
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:52,208
[mysterious music]

108
00:05:52,250 --> 00:06:00,000
♪ ♪

109
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:18,750
[explosion]

110
00:06:27,458 --> 00:06:30,917
[wood cracking]

111
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,542
- [grunts]

112
00:06:34,291 --> 00:06:36,959
[rocks clattering]

113
00:06:45,417 --> 00:06:48,375
[electrical booming]

114
00:06:48,417 --> 00:06:50,041
[cries and shouts]

115
00:06:50,083 --> 00:06:52,000
- AH! AH!

116
00:06:52,041 --> 00:06:54,959
[explosions and rubble falling]

117
00:06:59,834 --> 00:07:01,625
[glass shattering]

118
00:07:01,667 --> 00:07:04,208
AH! UH! UH!

119
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:05,166
[breathing heavily]

120
00:07:14,125 --> 00:07:16,500
- OPAL!

121
00:07:16,542 --> 00:07:18,333
[booming]

122
00:07:18,375 --> 00:07:21,542
[metal creaking]

123
00:07:26,542 --> 00:07:28,208
- EVERYONE, RETREAT.

124
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:30,500
TAKE THE WOUNDED BACK
TO ASAMI'S OFFICE.

125
00:07:30,542 --> 00:07:31,875
- I'LL MEET YOU THERE.

126
00:07:31,917 --> 00:07:33,625
I'M GOING TO SEE
IF I CAN FIND HELP.

127
00:07:35,041 --> 00:07:37,709
[explosion]

128
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:45,125
[somber music]

129
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:47,792
♪ ♪

130
00:07:47,834 --> 00:07:50,083
- ALL RIGHT.
LET'S FIRE IT UP AGAIN.

131
00:07:51,667 --> 00:07:52,709
[mechanical humming]

132
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,792
[engine rumbling]

133
00:07:54,834 --> 00:07:57,750
[wings fluttering]

134
00:08:01,083 --> 00:08:02,792
- I CAN'T STABILIZE IT!

135
00:08:02,834 --> 00:08:04,667
I THOUGHT YOU FIXED
THE HYDRAULICS.

136
00:08:04,709 --> 00:08:06,333
- I DID!

137
00:08:06,375 --> 00:08:07,792
TWIST HARDER!

138
00:08:07,834 --> 00:08:09,208
[mechanical grinding]

139
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,750
- AH-AH-OH!

140
00:08:14,792 --> 00:08:16,417
- I HOPE YOU HAVE SOMETHING
IN HERE

141
00:08:16,458 --> 00:08:18,125
THAT CAN TAKE OUT A PLATOON
OF MECHA-SUITS.

142
00:08:18,166 --> 00:08:20,500
KUVIRA'S TROOPS
ARE HEADED THIS WAY!

143
00:08:20,542 --> 00:08:22,959
- I KNOW HOW TO TAKE DOWN
SOME MECHA-SUITS,

144
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,417
AND IT JUST MIGHT TAKE DOWN
THAT GIANT, TOO!

145
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:28,417
ASAMI, DISCONNECT ANYTHING
ELECTRICAL IN HERE

146
00:08:28,458 --> 00:08:29,417
UNTIL WE GET BACK.

147
00:08:29,458 --> 00:08:30,750
ZHU LI, LET'S GO.

148
00:08:35,291 --> 00:08:37,208
- WHERE AM I?

149
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:38,542
MOM?

150
00:08:38,583 --> 00:08:40,041
- JUST REST, SON.

151
00:08:40,083 --> 00:08:41,041
I'M HERE.

152
00:08:41,083 --> 00:08:44,792
- MOM, I'M SO SORRY.

153
00:08:44,834 --> 00:08:48,375
I BETRAYED YOU--
THE WHOLE FAMILY.

154
00:08:48,417 --> 00:08:50,750
I GAVE MY LIFE TO KUVIRA,

155
00:08:50,792 --> 00:08:52,709
AND SHE JUST FIRED
THAT WEAPON AT ME.

156
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,792
HOW COULD SHE DO THAT?

157
00:08:54,834 --> 00:08:56,166
- I DON'T KNOW, SWEETIE.

158
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:58,333
SHE'S A COMPLICATED PERSON.

159
00:08:58,375 --> 00:09:01,458
- WING AND WEI WILL NEVER
FORGIVE ME.

160
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,041
AND OPAL...

161
00:09:03,083 --> 00:09:05,542
- YEAH, THEY MIGHT
TAKE SOME TIME TO COME AROUND,

162
00:09:05,583 --> 00:09:08,500
BUT WE'LL WORK THROUGH IT
AS A FAMILY.

163
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:14,333
- DO YOU THINK THIS PLAN
WILL ACTUALLY WORK, SIR?

164
00:09:14,375 --> 00:09:16,083
- I KNOW I CAN STOP
THE MECHA-SUITS

165
00:09:16,125 --> 00:09:19,000
WITH AN ELECTROMAGNETIC PULSE,
SO IT STANDS TO REASON

166
00:09:19,041 --> 00:09:21,041
THAT I CAN STOP
A GIANT MECHA-SUIT

167
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:23,417
WITH A GIANT
ELECTROMAGNETIC PULSE.

168
00:09:26,709 --> 00:09:28,542
ZHU LI, I'VE BEEN THINKING.

169
00:09:28,583 --> 00:09:30,333
- YOU'RE ALWAYS THINKING, SIR.

170
00:09:30,375 --> 00:09:34,125
- YES, BUT LATELY, '
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT YOU.

171
00:09:34,166 --> 00:09:36,750
I KNOW WE MIGHT NOT MAKE IT
OUT OF THIS MESS,

172
00:09:36,792 --> 00:09:39,291
AND I FEEL LIKE THERE ARE SOME
THINGS I SHOULD TELL YOU.

173
00:09:39,333 --> 00:09:40,583
- THERE ARE?

174
00:09:40,625 --> 00:09:42,166
- I REMEMBER WHEN I WAS A BOY,

175
00:09:42,208 --> 00:09:44,417
I HAD AN OSTRICH HORSE.

176
00:09:44,458 --> 00:09:46,291
NAMED HER MRS. BEAKS.

177
00:09:46,333 --> 00:09:47,875
I GREW UP ON A FARM.

178
00:09:47,917 --> 00:09:49,625
DID I EVER
TELL YOU THAT, ZHU LI?

179
00:09:49,667 --> 00:09:52,792
THIS WAS BEFORE THE CIRCUS
PEOPLE TOOK ME AWAY.

180
00:09:52,834 --> 00:09:58,041
ANYWAY, I LOVED OLD MRS. BEAKS,
BUT I TOOK HER FOR GRANTED.

181
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:00,250
- YOU'LL HAVE TO FINISH
YOUR STORY LATER.

182
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:02,959
KUVIRA'S TROOPS ARE IN RANGE.

183
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,917
OKAY. I HOPE THIS WORKS.

184
00:10:06,125 --> 00:10:09,125
[high-pitched buzzing]

185
00:10:09,166 --> 00:10:10,583
[mechanical grinding]

186
00:10:10,625 --> 00:10:13,709
[clanking and booming]

187
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:18,291
- YES! DEAD IN THEIR TRACKS.

188
00:10:18,333 --> 00:10:20,291
OH, RATS.

189
00:10:20,333 --> 00:10:22,333
SHE'S STILL COMING.

190
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:24,083
ZHU LI, DO THE THING!

191
00:10:24,125 --> 00:10:26,375
- I'M AFRAID
THERE ARE NO MORE THINGS TO DO.

192
00:10:28,333 --> 00:10:29,125
- WHAT WAS THAT?

193
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:30,917
- AN ELECTROMAGNETIC PULSE.

194
00:10:30,959 --> 00:10:33,458
IT SHUT DOWN THE MECHA-SUITS,
BUT OUR POWER SOURCE IS FINE.

195
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,750
- LOCATE THE SOURCE
OF THE PULSE.

196
00:10:34,792 --> 00:10:36,500
THAT MUST BE WHERE VARRICK IS.

197
00:10:36,542 --> 00:10:39,458
THIRD AND FOURTH MECH PLATOONS,
MOVE IN AND CONTINUE THE SWEEP.

198
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:42,417
CAPTURE ANYONE LEFT
IN THIS CITY.

199
00:10:42,458 --> 00:10:44,417
- VARRICK, HOW COME YOUR
ELECTRO-THINGY

200
00:10:44,458 --> 00:10:46,458
SHUT DOWN THE SMALL MECHA-SUITS
BUT NOT THE BIG ONE?

201
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,792
- BECAUSE IT'S POWERED
WITH SPIRIT VINE ENERGY.

202
00:10:48,834 --> 00:10:50,000
I'M SORRY.

203
00:10:50,041 --> 00:10:51,917
I WISH I COULD HELP YOU,

204
00:10:51,959 --> 00:10:53,500
BUT IT'S UNSTOPPABLE.

205
00:10:53,542 --> 00:10:56,291
- IT'S NOT.

206
00:10:56,333 --> 00:10:58,166
- DAD?

207
00:10:58,208 --> 00:10:59,875
- I GOT HIM OUT OF JAIL
TO HELP.

208
00:10:59,917 --> 00:11:01,542
I FIGURED
WE NEED ALL THE GENIUSES

209
00:11:01,583 --> 00:11:03,250
WE CAN GET OUR HANDS
ON RIGHT NOW.

210
00:11:03,291 --> 00:11:05,375
IF THE PRISON'S STILL STANDING
AFTER ALL THIS IS OVER,

211
00:11:05,417 --> 00:11:06,792
WE CAN THROW HIM
BACK IN.

212
00:11:06,834 --> 00:11:08,875
- I KNOW WHAT YOU ALL
MUST THINK OF ME,

213
00:11:08,917 --> 00:11:10,834
BUT I LOVE REPUBLIC CITY,

214
00:11:10,875 --> 00:11:12,792
AND I WOULD DO ANYTHING
TO SAVE HER.

215
00:11:12,834 --> 00:11:14,750
- YOU THINK YOU KNOW
HOW TO DEFEAT THIS THING?

216
00:11:14,792 --> 00:11:16,542
- YOU MUST ACT
LIKE AN INFECTION:

217
00:11:16,583 --> 00:11:18,875
BREAK THE SKIN AND ATTACK
THE VITAL ORGANS.

218
00:11:18,917 --> 00:11:20,750
DISCONNECT THE HEART
AND THE BRAIN,

219
00:11:20,792 --> 00:11:22,959
AND THIS BEAST CANNOT LIVE.

220
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,542
- BUT HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED
TO GET INSIDE?

221
00:11:24,583 --> 00:11:28,208
- FUTURE INDUSTRIES HAS PLASMA
SAWS FOR CUTTING PLATINUM.

222
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,959
IF WE HAD ONE
ON THE MECHA-SUIT...

223
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,083
- BUT THE SAWS ARE WAY TOO BIG.

224
00:11:32,125 --> 00:11:34,583
WE'D NEVER GET THE SUITS
OFF THE GROUND.

225
00:11:34,625 --> 00:11:36,500
- I THINK I CAN ADD
AN ELECTRICAL ELEMENT

226
00:11:36,542 --> 00:11:37,917
TO THE WELDING TORCH
ON YOUR SUIT

227
00:11:37,959 --> 00:11:39,917
AND CONVERT IT
INTO A PLASMA SAW.

228
00:11:39,959 --> 00:11:42,166
THEN WE'LL JUST HAVE
TO LAND ON THE GIANT

229
00:11:42,208 --> 00:11:44,834
AND CUT OPEN A HOLE BIG ENOUGH
FOR SOMEONE TO GET IN.

230
00:11:44,875 --> 00:11:46,750
- LIKE A METAL MOSQUITO.

231
00:11:46,792 --> 00:11:49,208
- YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS
TO MOSQUITOES THAT LAND ON ME?

232
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:50,834
I SQUASH 'EM!

233
00:11:50,875 --> 00:11:52,291
- WE'LL HAVE TO ATTACK
IN A SWARM

234
00:11:52,333 --> 00:11:54,625
TO TRY TO KEEP YOU GUYS SAFE
IN THE HUMMINGBIRD SUITS.

235
00:11:54,667 --> 00:11:57,125
IT LOOKS LIKE THEY'RE
OUR ONLY HOPE.

236
00:11:57,166 --> 00:11:59,709
- ♪ OH, FIRST HE ATE THE FRUIT ♪

237
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,375
♪ THEN HE ATE THE LEAVES ♪

238
00:12:01,417 --> 00:12:05,125
♪ HUNGRY LITTLE LEMUR
ATE UP ALL MY TREES ♪

239
00:12:05,166 --> 00:12:08,125
OKAY.
GREAT JOB, EVERYBODY.

240
00:12:08,166 --> 00:12:10,291
WHO'S GOT ANOTHER SONG FOR US?

241
00:12:10,333 --> 00:12:12,834
- WE CAN'T JUST SIT AROUND HERE
SINGING OLD AIRBENDER SONGS

242
00:12:12,875 --> 00:12:15,583
UNTIL WE'RE ALL CAPTURED
OR WORSE.

243
00:12:15,625 --> 00:12:17,291
- SHOULD WE PLAY
THE BUTTON GAME?

244
00:12:17,333 --> 00:12:18,458
WHO HAS A BUTTON?

245
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:21,417
[pounding]

246
00:12:27,333 --> 00:12:29,750
WHERE DID THESE BADGERMOLES
COME FROM?

247
00:12:29,792 --> 00:12:31,333
- THE ZOO!

248
00:12:31,375 --> 00:12:33,375
MAKO ALWAYS HATED MY SINGING,
BUT THEY LOVE IT!

249
00:12:33,417 --> 00:12:36,500
- WELL, WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED
TO DO WITH BADGERMOLES?

250
00:12:36,542 --> 00:12:38,250
- THEY'RE THE BEST
EARTHBENDERS AROUND!

251
00:12:38,291 --> 00:12:40,333
WE CAN USE THEM TO TUNNEL
OUT OF THE CITY

252
00:12:40,375 --> 00:12:41,959
WITHOUT KUVIRA'S TROOPS
SPOTTING US!

253
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:45,291
- ARE YOU SURE
THIS IS THE BEST PLAN?

254
00:12:45,333 --> 00:12:46,875
LET'S FOLLOW THE MOLES!

255
00:12:46,917 --> 00:12:49,125
- ♪ BADGERMOLES
DIGGING HOLES ♪

256
00:12:49,166 --> 00:12:51,041
♪ UNDER REPUBLIC CITY ♪

257
00:12:51,083 --> 00:12:52,917
♪ GOT TO RUN AWAY
FROM KUVIRA TODAY ♪

258
00:12:52,959 --> 00:12:54,959
♪ ALTHOUGH I DO STILL
THINK SHE'S PRETTY ♪

259
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:57,500
[plodding]

260
00:12:58,709 --> 00:13:00,333
- MECH PLATOONS, REPORT.

261
00:13:00,375 --> 00:13:03,000
- THIRD PLATOON.
NO SIGN OF ANYONE SO FAR.

262
00:13:03,041 --> 00:13:05,792
- FOURTH PLATOON.
EN ROUTE TO TRAIN STATION.

263
00:13:05,834 --> 00:13:09,125
- I THINK WE FOUND THE SOURCE
OF THE ELECTROMAGNETIC PULSE:

264
00:13:09,166 --> 00:13:10,667
FUTURE INDUSTRIES TOWER.

265
00:13:10,709 --> 00:13:12,542
- THAT'S THE PLACE.

266
00:13:12,583 --> 00:13:14,959
[mechanical buzzing]

267
00:13:16,041 --> 00:13:18,417
- KUVIRA IS HEADED OUR WAY.

268
00:13:18,458 --> 00:13:20,834
- HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE
TO GET THE PLASMA SAWS READY?

269
00:13:20,875 --> 00:13:22,083
- JUST A FEW MORE MINUTES.

270
00:13:22,125 --> 00:13:23,583
- GET OUT THERE
AS SOON AS YOU CAN.

271
00:13:23,625 --> 00:13:25,291
- IF YOU DO MANAGE
TO GET INSIDE,

272
00:13:25,333 --> 00:13:26,291
FIND THE ENGINE ROOM.

273
00:13:26,333 --> 00:13:27,875
THERE ARE TWO EMERGENCY LEVERS.

274
00:13:27,917 --> 00:13:29,458
IF YOU SWITCH THEM OFF
AT THE SAME TIME,

275
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,458
YOU'LL CUT THE POWER.

276
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,834
- THANKS.

277
00:13:31,875 --> 00:13:33,542
WE MAY NOT BE ABLE
TO BEAT THAT THING,

278
00:13:33,583 --> 00:13:34,875
BUT WE CAN SLOW IT DOWN.

279
00:13:34,917 --> 00:13:36,083
LET'S GO!

280
00:13:50,959 --> 00:13:53,917
[suspenseful music]

281
00:13:53,959 --> 00:14:01,959
♪ ♪

282
00:14:05,417 --> 00:14:07,083
[mechanical grinding]

283
00:14:09,417 --> 00:14:12,333
[electrical booming]

284
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:22,709
[rocks clattering]

285
00:14:25,458 --> 00:14:28,375
- [grunting]

286
00:14:48,125 --> 00:14:49,458
[fluttering]

287
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,917
[electrical booming]

288
00:15:12,208 --> 00:15:13,417
- JINORA!

289
00:15:21,834 --> 00:15:24,542
- [grunting]

290
00:15:25,792 --> 00:15:27,667
WHOA!

291
00:15:27,709 --> 00:15:28,875
OOH!

292
00:15:49,083 --> 00:15:51,250
- RAH!

293
00:15:51,291 --> 00:15:52,709
- [gasps]

294
00:15:58,041 --> 00:16:00,792
[crashing]

295
00:16:25,208 --> 00:16:27,041
- ♪ OH, YIN ♪

296
00:16:27,083 --> 00:16:31,667
♪ YOU'RE THE SWEETEST EVACUEE
I'VE EVER KNOWN ♪

297
00:16:31,709 --> 00:16:34,458
♪ AND I JUST WANT TO THANK YOU
FOR BEING SO KIND ♪

298
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:38,166
♪ WHEN I WAS LIVING
IN YOUR HOME ♪

299
00:16:38,208 --> 00:16:40,083
- HALT.

300
00:16:40,125 --> 00:16:43,125
TURN AROUND SLOWLY,
AND PLEASE, STOP THAT SINGING.

301
00:16:43,166 --> 00:16:45,667
YOU ARE ALL EARTH EMPIRE
PRISONERS.

302
00:16:45,709 --> 00:16:47,625
COME WITH US AND NO ONE
WILL GET HURT.

303
00:16:47,667 --> 00:16:49,291
- YOU DON'T NEED THESE PEOPLE.

304
00:16:49,333 --> 00:16:51,875
THEY'RE JUST INNOCENT CIVILIANS
CAUGHT IN THE CROSSFIRE,

305
00:16:51,917 --> 00:16:55,333
BUT I'M PRINCE WU, RIGHTFUL
LEADER OF THE EARTH KINGDOM.

306
00:16:55,375 --> 00:16:57,250
TAKE ME TO KUVIRA.

307
00:16:57,291 --> 00:16:58,959
I'VE GOT BUSINESS WITH HER.

308
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:00,250
- NO! DON'T DO IT, WU!

309
00:17:00,291 --> 00:17:01,917
- I HAVE TO.

310
00:17:01,959 --> 00:17:05,792
BUT BEFORE I GO, I'D LIKE
TO SING YOU A SONG.

311
00:17:05,834 --> 00:17:09,375
♪ IF YOU DON'T RESPECT
THE BROACH ♪

312
00:17:09,417 --> 00:17:12,542
♪ YOU DON'T RESPECT ME ♪

313
00:17:12,583 --> 00:17:15,834
♪ OH, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO ♪

314
00:17:15,875 --> 00:17:18,500
♪ YOU'RE NO BETTER
THAN A ROACH ♪

315
00:17:18,542 --> 00:17:21,417
♪ BUT I'M ROYALTY ♪

316
00:17:21,458 --> 00:17:25,083
♪ I GOT MY BADGERMOLES
WITH ME ♪

317
00:17:25,125 --> 00:17:29,125
- ACTUALLY, YOUR SONG IS SO BAD,
YOUR BADGERMOLES DESERTED YOU.

318
00:17:29,166 --> 00:17:31,625
- ♪ YOU DON'T KNOW ♪

319
00:17:31,667 --> 00:17:36,250
♪ WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT ♪

320
00:17:36,291 --> 00:17:38,709
[booming]

321
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:42,709
[growling]

322
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:45,792
♪ OH, BADGERMOLES
I LOVE YOU, I LOVE YOU ♪

323
00:17:45,834 --> 00:17:49,583
♪ I WANT TO, I WANT TO
PET YOUR SNOUTS ♪

324
00:17:51,041 --> 00:17:52,208
HA-HA!

325
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:53,458
[cheers]

326
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:55,875
[electrical humming]

327
00:17:55,917 --> 00:17:57,792
[clanking]

328
00:17:58,667 --> 00:18:01,083
- IF WE STOP THAT MECHA-GIANT,

329
00:18:01,125 --> 00:18:02,792
IT WILL ALL BE BECAUSE OF YOU.

330
00:18:02,834 --> 00:18:05,750
- YOU'RE THE ONE WHO DESIGNED
THESE INCREDIBLE SUITS.

331
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:09,291
IT'S GREAT TO BE WORKING
TOGETHER AGAIN.

332
00:18:09,333 --> 00:18:11,875
- I LOVE YOU, DAD.

333
00:18:11,917 --> 00:18:13,583
- I LOVE YOU, TOO.

334
00:18:18,041 --> 00:18:19,875
- ZHU LI?

335
00:18:19,917 --> 00:18:21,125
- YES?

336
00:18:21,166 --> 00:18:22,208
- [gulps]

337
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:24,000
I HAVE SOMETHING
I NEED TO ATTACH

338
00:18:24,041 --> 00:18:25,375
BEFORE WE TAKE OFF.

339
00:18:25,417 --> 00:18:26,917
- ATTACH TO WHAT?

340
00:18:26,959 --> 00:18:30,750
- I NEED TO ATTACH THIS RING
TO YOUR FINGER.

341
00:18:30,792 --> 00:18:34,291
ZHU LI MOON,
WILL YOU DO THE THING

342
00:18:34,333 --> 00:18:36,625
FOR THE REST OF OUR LIVES?

343
00:18:38,208 --> 00:18:40,208
- YES.

344
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:42,417
- YES!

345
00:18:44,792 --> 00:18:47,750
NOW, LET'S GO ATTACH THESE
BARELY-FUNCTIONAL RUST BUCKETS

346
00:18:47,792 --> 00:18:50,917
TO A GIANT
KILLER SMASHING MACHINE!

347
00:18:50,959 --> 00:18:54,417
- IT'S EXACTLY HOW I ALWAYS
PICTURED OUR ENGAGEMENT.

348
00:19:14,166 --> 00:19:16,834
[distant fluttering]

349
00:19:18,417 --> 00:19:21,125
[dramatic music]

350
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:28,000
♪ ♪

351
00:19:28,041 --> 00:19:30,500
- AIM FOR THAT SPOT
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE BACK,

352
00:19:30,542 --> 00:19:32,208
THE ONE I CAN NEVER REACH.

353
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,417
- GOT IT.

354
00:19:48,667 --> 00:19:50,291
- WHAA! LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

355
00:19:50,333 --> 00:19:51,291
[electrical buzzing]

356
00:19:51,333 --> 00:19:52,834
WOW!

357
00:19:52,875 --> 00:19:54,834
I WISH I HAD THAT KIND
OF FLEXIBILITY.

358
00:20:03,625 --> 00:20:06,834
[suspenseful music]

359
00:20:06,875 --> 00:20:14,792
♪ ♪

360
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:39,834
[beeping]

361
00:20:39,875 --> 00:20:40,792
- HANG ON!

362
00:20:43,834 --> 00:20:46,208
- AH!

363
00:20:46,250 --> 00:20:47,917
[explosion]

364
00:20:57,375 --> 00:20:59,041
- I NEED MORE POWER!

365
00:20:59,083 --> 00:21:00,291
THEY'RE CUTTING IN!

366
00:21:00,333 --> 00:21:01,417
MORE POWER!

367
00:21:01,458 --> 00:21:04,625
[mechanical grinding]

368
00:21:10,250 --> 00:21:12,875
[cracking]

369
00:21:12,917 --> 00:21:14,500
- WE NEED TO GET OUT OF HERE.

370
00:21:14,542 --> 00:21:16,875
- ALMOST THERE.

371
00:21:16,917 --> 00:21:17,834
- [gasps]

372
00:21:20,125 --> 00:21:21,500
- WE HAVE TO GO NOW!

373
00:21:21,542 --> 00:21:23,709
- ALMOST THERE. ALMOST THERE.

374
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,458
- DAD! NOW!

375
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:33,208
- GOOD-BYE, ASAMI.

376
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:34,834
I LOVE YOU.

377
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:38,709
- DAD!

378
00:21:47,542 --> 00:21:50,125
- HIROSHI'S PLAN WORKED.

379
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:51,875
THERE'S OUR OPENING.

380
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,750
- [grunting]
